<div class="welcome">
<p>WELCOME TO WROMIA!</p>
<p>The super fun and awesome self-closing open world,
that is like snake, but super fun and awesome.</p>
<p>You can control your worm with [UP], [DOWN],
[LEFT] and [RIGHT].</p>
<p>You can use utilize special abilities, obtained
by eating up strange points on the field with keys [1-5].</p>
<p>The dead have the special ability to respawn, so in
the highly likely case of dying, use [SPACE] to
respawn.</p>
<p>Gain points by eating certain dots, or by killing and
dismembering your fellow worms.</p>
<p>Become immortal by getting on the scoreboard on the right.</p>
